name: Boss Burger
description: Boss Burger was originally named by Matt Furie in 2014 & is featured in his new book, Cortex Vortex with a full page dedicated to him. The project was CTO'd by an all-star team who are having a ton of fun building community & making fan content of this hilarious quadrouple stack burger baddie on the blockchain. Here at #bossburger we’re building something rare. Not just a token. A crew. A digital backyard where everyone’s invited. We are building one order at a time.
